Class Motor

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscd211Classes.Motor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class Motor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Motor>
    A simple motor class that is being used for lab 1
    A motor contains a private String for the manufacturer and a double primitive for the watts produced by the motor.
